{"tid":103563,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ 朗拿甸奴：我+伊度奧+美斯勁過「MSN」","createTime":"2017-02-01T12:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T14:53:51.000Z","uid":3577,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3175a120938f69a405e7197b9b200b6347f2bd","tid":103563,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"回顧巴塞隊史，除了MSN之外，還有很多組非常優秀的進攻三叉戟，其間的比較更是少不了。在接受ESPN採訪時，朗拿甸奴就被問到了這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2683267.main_image.jpg?strip=all\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2F2683267.main_image.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall&h=75de8d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　「兩組三叉戟都創造了彼此的歷史，都做得很好，但我更喜歡我、伊度奧還有美斯組成的三叉戟。」在被問到與MSN組合的比較時，朗拿甸奴說道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　朗拿甸奴還特別稱讚了尼馬：「我認為尼馬已經躋身世界最佳球員的行列，有一天他會成為世界上最好的球員。我們巴西人都在等待這一天，因為他是全巴西足球圈的偶像。尼馬也是個很好的朋友，他成為世界最佳只是時間問題。」"},{"pid":"ea821bcf5a95854bf9afd7a35e92c17616e71dea","tid":103563,"uid":36232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"仲有享利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae77fa5b59c00cc96e4c923a8b3d2b9d4387b66","tid":103563,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有享利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伊度奧屌打回塘亨利"},{"pid":"760a2d65cc1799a75c10f131a92a452942c183d1","tid":103563,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"神奇四俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37fd17e050440343311f2da75513c4811710c19","tid":103563,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"吞精王伊度奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617e27a01d7813a6c4b438c1b1513c4eb279d989","tid":